\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {9}{\ignorespaces Consolidated empirical evidence for Theorems~\ref {thm:hpsmg-plus-app} and~\ref {thm:rate-separation}. (a) E2: bonus gap grows from $+0.14$ at $|\Theta _i|{=}2$ to $+1.08$ at $|\Theta _i|{=}6$ on Llama-Maverick, tracing the predicted $\Omega (|\Theta _i|^n)$-vs-$O(1)$ envelope of Theorem~\ref {thm:hpsmg-plus-app}(ii). (b) E3: bonus benefit grows monotonically with $n\!\in \!\{3,4,5\}$ while storage savings scale analytically as $|\Theta _i|^n/(n|\Theta _i|)$ ($43\times $ at $n{=}5$). (c) E5: per-episode cumulative-regret trajectories on HP-SPGG across four backbones; H-PSMG and H-PSMG\textsuperscript  {+} plateau at $<0.05$ regret per episode within $K{\approx }5$ (the $\tilde  O(\sqrt  K)$ envelope of Theorem~\ref {thm:main-regret-app}) while PSRL-NoType grows linearly ($0.50$--$0.93$ per episode), realising the rate separation of Theorem~\ref {thm:rate-separation} with cumulative gap $11$--$30\times $ at $K{=}20$. (d) E1: per-backbone posterior concentration time $K_{\mathrm  {conc}}^{0.9}$ (from vanilla H-PSMG, $\beta {=}0$) against the bonus benefit $\mathrm  {Reg}(\text  {H-PSMG})-\mathrm  {Reg}(\text  {H-PSMG}^{+})$ at $\beta {=}0.25$; the four backbones span the three regimes of Theorem~\ref {thm:hpsmg-plus-app} -- fastest-concentrating in self-decay edge, slowest in burn-in jump, intermediates in the high-$\beta $ boundary regime.}}{34}{figure.caption.31}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:e2-e5}{{9}{34}{Consolidated empirical evidence for Theorems~\ref {thm:hpsmg-plus-app} and~\ref {thm:rate-separation}. (a) E2: bonus gap grows from $+0.14$ at $|\Theta _i|{=}2$ to $+1.08$ at $|\Theta _i|{=}6$ on Llama-Maverick, tracing the predicted $\Omega (|\Theta _i|^n)$-vs-$O(1)$ envelope of Theorem~\ref {thm:hpsmg-plus-app}(ii). (b) E3: bonus benefit grows monotonically with $n\!\in \!\{3,4,5\}$ while storage savings scale analytically as $|\Theta _i|^n/(n|\Theta _i|)$ ($43\times $ at $n{=}5$). (c) E5: per-episode cumulative-regret trajectories on HP-SPGG across four backbones; H-PSMG and H-PSMG\textsuperscript {+} plateau at $<0.05$ regret per episode within $K{\approx }5$ (the $\tilde O(\sqrt K)$ envelope of Theorem~\ref {thm:main-regret-app}) while PSRL-NoType grows linearly ($0.50$--$0.93$ per episode), realising the rate separation of Theorem~\ref {thm:rate-separation} with cumulative gap $11$--$30\times $ at $K{=}20$. (d) E1: per-backbone posterior concentration time $K_{\mathrm {conc}}^{0.9}$ (from vanilla H-PSMG, $\beta {=}0$) against the bonus benefit $\mathrm {Reg}(\text {H-PSMG})-\mathrm {Reg}(\text {H-PSMG}^{+})$ at $\beta {=}0.25$; the four backbones span the three regimes of Theorem~\ref {thm:hpsmg-plus-app} -- fastest-concentrating in self-decay edge, slowest in burn-in jump, intermediates in the high-$\beta $ boundary regime}{figure.caption.31}{}}
