\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {13}{\ignorespaces SOTOPIA-Hard aggregate mean focal score per (backbone $\times $ baseline), $70$ episodes per cell. The five baselines cluster within a $0.12$-score envelope on every backbone; the per-backbone leader varies (ECON-BNE on DeepSeek, \texttt  {llm\_belief} on GPT-5.4-nano and Kimi-K2.6, A-ToM-1 on Llama-Maverick) and H-PSMG\textsuperscript  {+} stays within $0.1$ of the leader throughout but does not dominate -- consistent with the prior-factorisation lower bound (Theorem~\ref {thm:lower-no-pf}).}}{35}{figure.caption.39}\protected@file@percent }
